" open terminal
nnoremap <silent> vp :call neoterm#open()<CR><C-w>w
" hide/close terminal
nnoremap <silent> vc :call neoterm#toggle()<CR>
" kills the current job (send a <c-c>)
nnoremap <silent> vq :call neoterm#kill()<CR>

autocmd WinEnter term://* startinsert

command! Rails   :T bin/rails s
command! Rspec   :T bin/rspec

command! Django  :T python manage.py runserver
command! DjangoT :T python manage.py test
